---
title: Mexican Cheesy Bean Quesadillas with Chipotle Sour Cream & Pickled Salsa
description: Red kidney beans and charred corn unite to make a hearty and delicious filling for these quesadillas. Simply spoon the filling onto tortillas and fold them in half, then sprinkle with cheese and bake. Easy cheesy dinner coming right up!
